<br>
Rather than a petition which won't work anyways, why don't we actually try to get these things done working together.<br>
<br>
I know it doesn't seem fair to some, but I for one hate grouping with a cleric, seeing another cleric in the zone then having my group's cleric say &quot;god I hate that person. she/he stole ragefire from me&quot;. <br>
<br>
This is a rather small issue, but in the long run it won't help us any when clerics don't like each other because of the ragefire thing.<br>
<br>
What I would *like* to see, and probably won't happen, is the clerics who are camping ragefire do so, and when he spawns, have a list of people willing to help ready to go. I'm not talking about just thier guilds, I'm talking about any random person willing to help get ragefire down. When it's all done, we random the heart off to the participating clerics who were there camping it, and the process starts again.<br>
This brings up another problem, where people don't have the time to sit there for hours. Or days.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure how to solve this with the best results, but if ANY cleric needs help with ragefire, look me up, and send me a tell. I will drop anything I'm doing (if possible) and come help.<br>
